A MAN has been killed in a two-vehicle smash on the A90 Dundee to Perth Road.
The accident, which happened near Kinfauns at 3.10pm today, is reported to have involved a white Mercedes van and a lorry.
Firefighters, paramedics and police were quickly at the scene on the southbound carriageway following the collision.
